{
  "chapter": 18,
  "chapter_summary": "乌氏倮得知赵王奸细名单后决定叛离赵国，部署撤退计划，召义子乌卓率千人死士来邯郸。项少龙编造桑林村出身假故事，陶方安排假扮村民掩饰。婚礼推迟一个月以掩饰行动。项少龙与乌廷芳搬入隐龙居同居，婷芳氏亦随之迁入。当晚项少龙赴赵穆侯府，赵穆试探其出身，项少龙如实交代与元宗相遇经过。墨者巨子严平现身，确认项少龙未获巨子令传人身份。赵穆以名利笼络项少龙，要他背叛乌家效忠赵国，并赠越国名剑飞虹和越国孪生姊妹田贞、田凤以施恩。项少龙虚与委蛇，暗中思索如何为元宗报仇雪恨。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "speaker_name": "乌氏倮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "虽说赵雅可信性极高，但我们仍须以种种手法查证名单的真伪，这事交由应元负责。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "speaker_name": "乌氏倮",
      "listener": "char_tao_fang",
      "text": "你立即派人兼程赶往桑林村，把美蚕娘迁往秘密地方，再以重金收买那里的人，要他们为少龙说谎，掩饰他乃秦人之后的秘密。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我一向在深山打猎维生，只是最近才到桑林村去，一直住在偏僻的山谷里……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这个没有问题，我会使人假扮村民，应付查询，保证不会被人识破。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "speaker_name": "乌氏倮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今天全仗少龙，我们才清楚形势险恶到这地步，若非少龙昨晚获胜，教连晋娶得芳儿就糟了。由现在起，我乌氏倮再不视自己为赵国人，幸好我们和各国的权贵向有交往，逃到哪里都有人接纳，问题是怎样避过赵人的追杀？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "speaker_name": "乌氏倮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "秋收结账的时间已到，趁各地牧场主管来邯郸之际，我会趁机部署一下，准备好应变的措施，他不仁，我不义，孝成王想对付我，我就顺势把他拖垮。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "养兵千日，用在一时。现在应是召乌卓和他训练的死士来邯郸的紧急时刻了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "乌卓是主人的义子，专在各地收养无父无母的孤儿，加以严格的训练，作为我们的核心主力，人数在千人间，平时分散在邯郸附近各牧场，知道此事的人就只我们几个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有他们来助少龙，更是如虎添翼，就算赵王派人来攻打我们乌家城堡，我们仍可以守他十天半月。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "speaker_name": "乌氏倮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们把少龙和芳儿的婚礼推迟到一个月后，如此我们可借筹备婚礼，掩饰各式各样的行动。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老仆还可以假借重组武黑的手下为名做出调动，把大部分内奸调离这里，不教赵人起疑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "speaker_name": "乌氏倮",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "就这么办。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "speaker_name": "乌氏倮",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙要扮作利欲熏心的样子，接受赵穆的笼络，更要扮作沉迷于赵雅的美色，教赵人不起疑心。我们会把一些资料让你泄露给赵人，使他们更信任你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "speaker_name": "乌氏倮",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "去见芳儿吧！她刚来向我们要人呢！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "有什么好奇怪的，廷芳早是你的人，爹和娘又不反对，我自然要搬来与你同住。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "text": "有权利就有义务，每晚我都要你付足床第税才准睡觉。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ting_fang_shi",
      "speaker_name": "婷芳氏",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "孙小姐说西厢八间房，头房是我的，其他留给你将来纳回来的女人，若不够用，还可教人加盖一座。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ting_fang_shi",
      "text": "开心吗？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ting_fang_shi",
      "speaker_name": "婷芳氏",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "听说她们有些被送去当营妓，除我之外没有人留在乌府。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "芳儿的寝室布置得舒服吗？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "text": "我最欣赏是那张大床。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "今晚你宴罢归来，记得爬上来啊！人家不睡觉等你。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "text": "来！让我服侍你这美人入浴。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙剑法显得受明师指点，不知令师何人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这就是现在邯郸墨者行馆的巨子严平先生，也是我王的客卿，他适才坐在隔壁，少龙的话他全听到了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_ping",
      "speaker_name": "严平",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "兵卫大人能击败连晋，显已得我墨门叛徒元宗的真传，只不知他的巨子令是否一并传给你？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_yan_ping",
      "text": "什么巨子令？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_ping",
      "speaker_name": "严平",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "本子也相信元宗不会把巨子令交给一个外人。不过对于他为何将剑术传给兵卫大人，本子仍是想不通。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_yan_ping",
      "text": "巨子凭何认定少龙不是巨子令的传人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_ping",
      "speaker_name": "严平",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "我们墨者身体力行的是节约和刻苦之道，居室茅茨不剪，用的是土簋土碗，饮的是藜藿的羹，吃的是粗糙的高粱饭，穿的是葛布、鹿皮。若元宗肯传他巨子令，自因他已成为墨者。可是兵卫大人不戒女色、酒食，显然尚非我墨门之人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "本侯非常欣赏少龙这种坦诚无私的态度。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "假若刚才少龙说的是谎言，现在怕已溅血此轩了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "多谢侯爷信任。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_yan_ping",
      "text": "元宗先生对鄙人有传艺之恩，不知他现在去向如何？当日他忽然着我离开武安，又不肯与我同行，鄙人便觉得有点不妥，那时我还不知他与墨门有关系。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_ping",
      "speaker_name": "严平",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不知道最好，兵卫最好以后都不要过问我们墨者的事。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "巨子身份尊崇，手下三百死士，人人剑术高明，可以一当百，巨子本身更是高手里的高手，连见到大王都不用执君臣之礼，对少龙算是客气的了！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙的表现令本侯非常满意，所以本侯再不见外，坦白和少龙说出心中的想法。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "对本侯来说，这世上的人是敌则非友，是友则非敌。假设你是我的人，我可保你金钱美女、权势地位享之不尽。但若成了我的敌人，本侯将不择手段把你毁掉。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "少龙明白！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙莫怪我看走眼，拣了连晋，才使出手段对付你，哪知仍低估了你。到现在本侯仍不明白为何你被喂下烈性春药，神智竟不受影响，能反败为胜？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "我这人最是好色，加上甚受女性欢迎，有时应付不来，只好借助春药，开始时一、两粒即立竿见影，用多了，非大量服食不可，所以不大怕这类东西。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "原来如此，不过你确是天赋异禀，如此鬼混仍有这么好的体魄。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙以前是乌氏家臣，可以不论。但现在成为大王的贴身兵卫，自须公私分明，事事应以我大赵为重，少龙明白本侯的意思吗？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "少龙自然懂得分辨谁才是应该尽忠的对象，侯爷请放心。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我会找几件事来试试你，只要证实你的忠诚，本侯会向大王竭力推荐，保证你前途无限，建爵封侯，亦非妄想。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "快起来，今晚的公事至此为止，接着便是享乐的时光了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙拣姊姊还是妹妹？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "不会有什么分别吧！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "说到铸剑，没有人能胜过越国的剑匠，第一把铁剑便是由他们铸成，经他们淬火后多番锻打而成的剑，性能远超前代体短质脆的青铜剑。我手上这把越剑名'飞虹'，本侯因看你的木剑沉重非常，不便携带，所谓宝剑赠侠士，今夜就把此剑送你。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "田贞",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "越国女子田贞、田凤拜见项兵卫。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "宝剑、美人，我看少龙还是中意后者居多。但不若先看剑吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "平时一点分别都没有，但到了榻上，分别就出现了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_tian_zhen",
      "text": "给我站起来，脱掉衣服。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你看，只有越女的身体才会像她们这样，似随风飘摇的嫩草一样袅娜多姿，我们的赵女稍嫌胖了点，只有乌廷芳和赵雅等几个是罕有的例外。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "嘿！侯爷，卑职想去方便一下，喝得太多酒哩！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_tian_zhen",
      "text": "姊姊陪少龙去吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tian_zhen",
      "text": "放下它！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 378
    }
